cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new conditioning mechanism for leveraging guidance images, which involves feature transformations and could be considered a machine learning approach (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves some geometric transformations, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
